OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FHeavy
OL,6,Fshowers at first but these dying out
OL,7,Ffor a time. Further showers will then
OL,8,Fspread east overnight but the east
OL,9,Fcoast should stay mainly dry.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FA largely cloudy day with
OL,12,Fbright spells and showers, some of
OL,13,Fthese could be heavy.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FHeavy
OL,16,Fand thundery showers on Wednesday then
OL,17,Fcloudy with outbreaks of rain
OL,18,Fspreading east on Wednesday. Bright
OL,19,Fand breezy with scattered showers on
OL,20,FFriday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
